        "subject": "LU-5197 mdt: try to return layout lock on open",
        "message": "LU-5197 mdt: try to return layout lock on open\n\nIn mdt_object_open_lock() use a local lock handle (MDT_LH_LOCAL) only\nwhen we need to revoke a lease. This unbotches the handling of\ntry_layout introduced by the fix for LU-4398 mdt: acquire an open lock\nfor write or execute (708d85a652a77f85153790e6cca1b7a2b91947cf).\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ide855f0b3fe2b8418fc4af8a4cf64ff5eb60e233\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
